Fixes #999 

Allows a default proxy to be configured through `Config/client.json`

```json
{
    "proxy": {
        "hostname": "google.com", 
        "port": 80,
        "securityLayer": "none"
    }
}
```

For the above example, all requests sent to `drop.client.get(...)` would be proxied through google.com.
